</sense> <sense n="f" xml:id="T1Xf"><foreign xml:lang="gez">በዓለ፡ ነጋሪት፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote>baʿāla nagārit</quote></cit> <lbl expand="literally">lit.</lbl> ‘an owner of kettledrum’ a person in power <foreign xml:lang="gez">በዓለ፡ ነጋሪት፡ የሚሰጠው ነው፡ ፩፡ አሞሌ፡ የፈረስ፡ ከሀገር፡ ግዛት።</foreign> ‘<cit type="translation" xml:lang="fr"><quote>ce que le gouverneur doit donner, sur le gouvernement du pays, c’est 1 amolē par cheval.</quote></cit>’ <bibl><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1909LiberT"/><citedRange unit="page"> 55 l. 22–23 (ed.)</citedRange></bibl>, <bibl><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1910LiberV"/><citedRange unit="page"> 67 l. 9–11 (tr.)</citedRange></bibl>, <lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነጋሪት፡</foreign> 
